# Keep the Cloud Build context small and prevent local secrets/artifacts from
# ever being copied into an image layer (OPS-3).
.git
.github
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.env
**/.env.*
.npmrc
docs
# NOTE: do NOT ignore `deploy/`. `gcloud builds submit` filters the uploaded
# source with this .dockerignore (no .gcloudignore present), and the build runs
# `docker build -f deploy/gcp/Dockerfile .`. Ignoring `deploy/` strips the
# Dockerfile from the upload and the build fails before it starts. The Dockerfile
# COPYs nothing under deploy/, so keeping it costs only a few KB of context.
**/test
*.md
mcp-publisher
mcp-publisher.exe
